LDAP Cohort Synchronization

The plugin synchronizes LDAP groups including users  with Moodle, creating Cohorts and enrolling users into them.

New install
-----------
1. Copy the folder ldapcohorts inside your /moodle/enrol folder.


Update
--------------------------------------------------
1. Overwrite the files in the /moodle/enrol/ldapcohorts directory with the new files.

2. From the admin page, click on the 'Notifications' link - the plugin will be automatically updated.